---
// Problem V7 — Structure Constat / Problème, logos locaux colorés
---

<section class="py-24" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- ── CONSTAT ── -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-20">

      <!-- Texte gauche -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4" style="color: var(--accent);">Le constat</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
          Des dizaines d'outils.<br />
          <span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Mais pas de stratégie.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-3" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">58% des dirigeants de PME</strong> considèrent l'IA comme un enjeu de survie. Mais autant n'ont encore aucune stratégie en place.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.francenum.gouv.fr/magazine-du-numerique/lia-dans-les-pme-et-eti-francaises-une-revolution-tranquille"
          target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-xs hover:opacity-80 transition underline underline-offset-2"
          style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
          Bpifrance Le Lab · 1 200 dirigeants PME-ETI · 2025 ↗
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Logos flottants droite -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-right">
        <div class="logos-chaos relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 1/1; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 30%, rgba(59,130,246,0.08), transparent 60%), linear-gradient(135deg, #080d1a, #0a1020); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 text-center pointer-events-none" style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); text-transform: uppercase;">Vos outils · sans stratégie</div>

          <div class="logo-item" style="top:7%; left:10%; animation-delay:0s;    --glow:rgba(16,185,129,0.45);  --c:#10b981;"><img src="/icons/chatgpt.svg"   class="logo-svg" alt="ChatGPT"  width="42" height="42"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:5%; left:50%; animation-delay:0.8s;  --glow:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);  --c:#ffffff;"><img src="/icons/notion.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Notion"    width="36" height="36"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:4%; right:8%; animation-delay:1.6s;  --glow:rgba(255,74,0,0.5);     --c:#ff4a00;"><img src="/icons/zapier.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Zapier"    width="40" height="40"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:28%;left:4%;  animation-delay:2.2s;  --glow:rgba(96,165,250,0.4);   --c:#60a5fa;"><img src="/icons/anthropic.svg" class="logo-svg" alt="Claude"    width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:26%;left:36%; animation-delay:0.4s;  --glow:rgba(155,89,182,0.5);   --c:#9b59b6;"><img src="/icons/make.svg"      class="logo-svg" alt="Make"      width="38" height="38"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:24%;right:6%; animation-delay:1.2s;  --glow:rgba(0,196,204,0.4);    --c:#00c4cc;"><img src="/icons/canva.svg"     class="logo-svg" alt="Canva"     width="36" height="36"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:52%;left:16%; animation-delay:1.8s;  --glow:rgba(239,83,80,0.4);    --c:#ef5350;"><img src="/icons/n8n.svg"       class="logo-svg" alt="n8n"       width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:54%;left:50%; animation-delay:0.6s;  --glow:rgba(66,133,244,0.5);   --c:#4285f4;"><img src="/icons/gemini.svg"    class="logo-svg" alt="Gemini"    width="38" height="38"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:50%;right:5%; animation-delay:2.5s;  --glow:rgba(255,122,89,0.4);   --c:#ff7a59;"><img src="/icons/hubspot.svg"   class="logo-svg" alt="HubSpot"   width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:74%;left:6%;  animation-delay:1.4s;  --glow:rgba(24,191,255,0.3);   --c:#18bfff;"><img src="/icons/airtable.svg"  class="logo-svg" alt="Airtable"  width="32" height="32"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:76%;left:42%; animation-delay:0.2s;  --glow:rgba(231,29,54,0.4);    --c:#e71d36;"><img src="/icons/slack.svg"     class="logo-svg" alt="Slack"     width="34" height="34"/></div>
          <div class="logo-item" style="top:72%;right:8%; animation-delay:2.0s;  --glow:rgba(251,191,36,0.35);  --c:#fbbf24;"><img src="/icons/perplexity.svg" class="logo-svg" alt="Perplexity" width="32" height="32"/></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── PROBLÈME ── -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 reveal" style="color: var(--accent);">Le problème</div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-10 reveal">
        Vous vous reconnaissez<span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);"> là-dedans ?</span>
      </h3>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-1" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-rose-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #f87171;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #f87171;">−8h / sem.</div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Du temps perdu sur des outils non cadrés</h4>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">CRM, agent IA, refonte site, LinkedIn... Tout part en même temps. Vos équipes testent, abandonnent, recommencent. Le ROI reste introuvable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-2" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #fbbf24;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #fbbf24;">−2 000 € / an</div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Des abonnements qui ne servent à rien</h4>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">ChatGPT, Zapier, Notion, Make, HubSpot... Chaque outil coûte 30 à 100 € par mois. Sans cadrage, vous payez pour des outils que personne n'utilise vraiment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl card-hover reveal reveal-delay-3" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #818cf8;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #818cf8;">0 résultat</div>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Des projets IA qui n'aboutissent pas</h4>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Automatisation lancée sans diagnostic. Processus automatisé qui était déjà cassé. Mois de travail pour un outil que les équipes n'adoptent pas.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── PONT VERS LA SOLUTION ── -->
    <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl reveal" style="background: var(--bg-primary); border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.2);">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-lg font-serif italic leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
          "L'IA n'est pas une solution. C'est un levier — et seulement si le problème est bien posé en amont."
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold" style="color: var(--accent);">C'est exactement là qu'intervient le cadrage. ↓</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .logo-item {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    animation: logo-float 7s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 22px -6px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.3));
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .logo-item:hover {
    transform: scale(1.15) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 0 32px -4px var(--glow, rgba(96,165,250,0.5));
    z-index: 10;
  }
  /* Colorisation SVG via filter CSS */
  .logo-svg {
    display: block;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(1);
    opacity: 0.85;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .logo-item:hover .logo-svg { opacity: 1; }

  @keyframes logo-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    25%       { transform: translateY(-9px) rotate(2deg); }
    75%       { transform: translateY(6px) rotate(-2deg); }
  }
</style>
